S.FORM: Mohammed VI of Morocco I 1963 a miheca saka 8 folad saka 21 a romi'ad masofoc ci Mohammed VI of Morocco, malamikomoday a tamdaw. O Sawara'an no kitakit no Morocco anini i ci Mohammed VI of Morocco, patirengan a romi'ad i 1999 a miheca saka 6 folad saka 23 a romi'ad. Itiyaay ho a 'orip 早期生活 Hongti no Morocco 摩洛哥的國王 misafangcal ato mipakonira to 'orip 社會改革及自由化
